		    <title outputclass="H305" class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">507.105</ph> Contents of acquisition plans.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d144e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li props="Runin"
                otherprops="abc"
                outputclass="H5_abcRunIn"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d142e17" outputclass="H5_abcRunIn" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						              <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Written</i>.</p>
					          <ol id="d144e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e30" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The APW contains the format prescribed in FAR 7.105 and shall be used in the preparation of acquisition plans. Where a particular element described in FAR 7.105 does not apply, the acquisition plan should read “not applicable.” The dollar value, complexity (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, commercial versus non-commercial item) and method of acquisition (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, full and open competition versus task/delivery order) of the supplies and services to be acquired will affect the scope and breadth of the acquisition plan.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e45" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 FAR 7.106 (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">major systems</i>) and FAR 7.107 (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">consolidation, bundling</i>, or <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">substantial bundling</i>) shall be addressed in the plans, if applicable.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e63" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 For leasehold interests in real property, a modified version of the contents of acquisition plans for leases is provided in the APW.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e72" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The requirement for a written plan may be waived by the appropriate level of an approving official listed in GSAM 507.105(c). When the requirement for a written plan is waived, an oral plan is still required. The planner must obtain approval for the oral plan from the approving official.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="id18C790U0N8K" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Software</i>. If procuring software, specify the result of any software requirement alternatives analysis that has been completed in accordance with <xref href="GSAM-i1890257.dita#i1890257"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">511.002</xref>(d).</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d142e83" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						              <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Oral plans</i>. Oral plans are only authorized by approval of the HCA and may be used in unusual and compelling situations. The planner shall document a summary of the oral plan, and shall also include: the name and signature of the approving official; the date the oral plan was approved; and the reason for waiving a written plan. The summary shall be included in the official contract file. In addition, the summary should be a part of, or attached to, any justification for other than full and open competition as required by FAR 6.302, or in the basis for using an exception to the fair opportunity process required by FAR 16.505(b)(2). The summary may be prepared after award if preparation before award would unreasonably delay the award, such as in the case of circumstances warranting the use of a letter contract.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin"
                otherprops="abc"
                outputclass="H5_abcRunIn"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d142e95" outputclass="H5_abcRunIn" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						              <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Approval thresholds</i>.</p>
					          <ol id="d144e104" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e108" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The following are the dollar value thresholds and the level of the approving official for approving acquisition plans or waiving written plans. For purposes of leasing, the Simplified Leasing Acquisition Threshold (SLAT) is defined in <xref href="GSAM-SSQFWIXN.dita#SSQFWIXN"
                              outputclass="fm:Part"
                              class="- topic/xref ">part  570</xref>. The HCA may authorize higher level approving officials for the thresholds set out below.</p>
							              <table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
								                <tgroup cols="2"
                                colsep="1"
                                rowsep="1"
                                outputclass="Notitle_rule"
                                class="- topic/tgroup ">
									                  <colspec colnum="1"
                                    colname="1"
                                    colwidth="50*"
                                    class="- topic/colspec "
                                    rowheader="headers"/>
									                  <colspec colnum="2"
                                    colname="2"
                                    colwidth="50*"
                                    class="- topic/colspec "
                                    rowheader="headers"/>
									                  <thead class="- topic/thead ">
										                    <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
											                      <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellHead_CBottom"
                                       outputclass="CellHead_CBottom"
                                       xtrc="CBottom"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Threshold</p>
											                      </entry>
											                      <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellHead_CBottom"
                                       outputclass="CellHead_CBottom"
                                       xtrc="CBottom"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Approving Official</p>
											                      </entry>
										                    </row>
									                  </thead>
									                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
										                    <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
											                      <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Below the SAT</p>
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">(SLAT for leases)</p>
											                      </entry>
											                      <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Contracting Officer</p>
											                      </entry>
										                    </row>
										                    <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
											                      <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">SAT (SLAT for leases) to,</p>
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">and including, $6 million</p>
											                      </entry>
											                      <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">One Level above the Contracting Officer</p>
											                      </entry>
										                    </row>
										                    <row rowsep="1" class="- topic/row ">
											                      <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Over $6 million to,</p>
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">and including, $20 million</p>
											                      </entry>
											                      <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Contracting Director</p>
											                      </entry>
										                    </row>
										                    <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
											                      <entry colname="1" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">Over $20 million</p>
											                      </entry>
											                      <entry colname="2" class="- topic/entry ">
												                        <p otherprops="CellBody_9"
                                       outputclass="CellBody_9"
                                       xtrc="9pt"
                                       class="- topic/p ">HCA</p>
											                      </entry>
										                    </row>
									                  </tbody>
								                </tgroup>
							              </table>
							              <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
								                <p outputclass="Note" class="- topic/p ">Note: Thresholds shall include all options.</p>
							              </note>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e228" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 If the acquisition meets one of the following criteria and is greater than the SAT, the planner must obtain HCA approval of the plan:</p>
							              <ol id="d144e234" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e238" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Complex, critical to agency strategic objectives and mission, highly visible or politically sensitive.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e247" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     An acquisition with which GSA has little or no experience that may result in a need for greater oversight or risk management.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e256" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Actions using significantly changed methods (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i>, methods of procurement such as lease versus purchase, or methods of performance such as contractor versus Government personnel).</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e268" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iv)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     New construction or repair, lease prospectus and alteration prospectus budget line items.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e277" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(v)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Any acquisition that involves–</p>
									                  <ol id="d144e283" class="- topic/ol ">
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e287" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(A)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Consolidation above $2 million (FAR 7.107-2); or</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e296" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(B)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Bundling at any dollar value (FAR 7.107-3)</p>
										                    </li>
									                  </ol>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li id="i1892459"
                      otherprops="123"
                      outputclass="H6_123"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d142e309" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Acquisitions requiring additional transactional data reporting elements to those listed in subparagraph (b)(2) of clauses <xref href="GSAM-i1876737.dita#i1876737"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">552.216-75</xref> and <xref href="GSAM-i1873910.dita#i1873910"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">552.238-74</xref> Alternate I–</p>
							              <ol id="d144e321" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e325" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     Must be coordinated with the applicable category manager, and obtain approval by the HCA and Senior Procurement Executive; and</p>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e334" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     All of the following information must be included in the rationale for adding transactional data reporting elements:</p>
									                  <ol id="d144e340" class="- topic/ol ">
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e344" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(A)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         List of the data element(s) to be collected.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e353" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(B)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Describe how the information will be used.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e362" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(C)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Describe the method of submission (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">e.g.</i> which information technology system will be used, what format(s) are acceptable).</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e374" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(D)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Address any potential duplication (<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">i.e</i>. does the contractor submit this data in any other method already?).</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e386" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(E)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Describe efforts to minimize burden on small business.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e396" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(F)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Describe consequence to Federal program if the element(s) are not collected.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e405" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(G)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Describe alternatives to obtaining the information other than collecting it from the contractor through this clause.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e414" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(H)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Identify whether or not this data will be made publicly available and the rationale for this decision, and how the information will be published, if applicable.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e423" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(I)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Estimated annual burden to the public in terms of hours. The estimate should indicate the number of contractors expected to report the data, frequency of reporting, annual hour burden, and an explanation of how the burden was estimated.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e432" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(J)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Estimated annual cost to the public in terms of dollars. The estimate should be broken out by initial setup costs and the cost to maintain the reporting requirement.</p>
										                    </li>
										                    <li otherprops="H8_ABC" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/li ">
											                      <p id="d142e441" outputclass="H8_ABC" class="- topic/p ">
                                    <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(K)</ph>
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
                                    
												                         Estimated total annual cost to the government.</p>
										                    </li>
									                  </ol>
								                </li>
								                <li otherprops="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii"
                            class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d142e452" outputclass="H7_i_ii_iii" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                     The approval requirements in this subparagraph do not apply to additional data elements added to a task/delivery order or blanket purchase agreement. However, coordination with the applicable category manager is required.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
